dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Populated Admin0 name field with UN Short Name "Comoros (the)". 2. Created and populated reference name field.
The following was found by ITOS but not addressed in this version: 1. The parentheses in some names suggests the presence of AltNames that should be separated and placed in an AltName field.
